{"tid":1502729,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[ios/Android][SRWDD]超級機械人大戰DD","createTime":"2019-08-24T17:12:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T12:06:46.000Z","uid":77269,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2d33561cfe406df96968b61ff269d801d9400000","tid":1502729,"uid":77269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:12:46.000Z","msg":"機戰DD 首抽刷甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n《機戰DD》是免費遊戲，進入版圖戰鬥也不消耗「心心」等items，那BANDAI如何賺錢？原來遊戲中取得機體只得1招基本攻擊，如果你不抽蛋增加招式，你根本不可能過版。<br />\n<br />\n抽蛋《機戰DD》抽的正是：單純增加能力的「特殊能力配件」，以及加能力外再為機體加招式的「招式／必殺技配件」。但留意後者必須安裝在相應機體，招式才會有效，最理想當然是刷中最強的SSR超必殺技配件如：《勇者王》風起雲動拳、《獨角獸高達》NT-D連續攻擊等。但它們需要3－4 TURN儲氣才能發動，所以你還需要抽一些SR基本招，要爆機還是得花錢。<br />\n<br />\n(中獎機率：保證SR以上的1次為：SSR 3%／SR 97%，此外為：SSR 3% / SR 15% / R 82%)<br />\n來源：香港01"},{"pid":"607fa4939cab16eb7d738846e020057a44b23633","tid":1502729,"uid":77269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:15:45.000Z","msg":"唔喺好識開Game po，見出左幾日都未有po未開下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然隻game好失望，但機戰撚必須支付下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3825ff9d3f8b167574a7c25b05e6b3878209ca96","tid":1502729,"uid":208095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:32:33.000Z","msg":"玩咗幾日都無見人開po，應該都係垃圾game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2de2285b74de71811fe4411e2007b0d49d84fc2","tid":1502729,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:39:22.000Z","msg":"就咁睇介紹都覺得係垃圾"},{"pid":"b8709f79fc9b5d68f8d71c674022b2e887f6a0a9","tid":1502729,"uid":77269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T22:58:48.000Z","msg":"其實幾撚失望下"},{"pid":"5bd6f337b9add928f442f1669646cdaea2602a83","tid":1502729,"uid":49182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3825ff9d3f8b167574